    <title>A Model of Global Currency Pricing</title>
    <updated>2025-03-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Michael B. Devereux, Rui Lu, Kang Shi &amp; Juanyi (Jenny) Xu</name>
